Package edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.manager

Class RegistrationManager

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.manager.RegistrationManager
public class RegistrationManager extends Object
Class for handling Registration information. Will accept a Registrar user and will allow a logged-in Registrar to manage the course catalog and the student directory.
Author:
Jeremiah Knizley, Spencer Grattan
